{"tid":1076971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【我知我肥】我係要玩cosplay","createTime":"2019-03-25T08:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T10:02:30.000Z","uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2e4894e161efff9fa70de590acf405cdd6f669","tid":1076971,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"現時體重七十公斤的雪月是忠實Cosplay愛好者，卻因為身材豐滿飽受冷嘲熱諷：「我無論多輕多重也被人叫肥妹，那我為何要節制自己﹖所以後期已自暴自棄。」Cosplay非主流文化，肥胖的角色扮演者更是少眾中之少眾，雪月敢當其中一份子，苦樂交纏的感受，只有她最清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20160119/large/18grennew3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160119%2Flarge%2F18grennew3.jpg&h=25479467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCosplay療瘉自卑寂寞<br />\n<br />\n諷刺的是，雪月當初沉迷cosplay，多少為了逃避批判眼光。她自小個性自卑，曾因討厭自己而自殘發洩：「照鏡就想摑自己兩巴，同自己講不如死了算！你又不美，又肥，為甚麼要生存在世上？」讀書年代，自卑變成乖戾，她常攻擊別人以保護自己，以致朋友寥寥無幾。<br />\n<br />\n就在最寂寞的時候，恰巧有動漫同好邀她玩cosplay，豈料一試成癮，結果高峰時期一星期可以玩上五天。「我也覺得是病態，很瘋狂，現在看回是有點想逃避現實。」零自信的她，每當披上角色服裝便判若兩人，有型「甫士」長擺長有，雙眼更會「放電」。問她差異何以這麼大，她微笑回應：「穿起這衣服，便覺得我不再是自己，已經投入了角色。」雪月特別鍾愛一個頑皮小女孩的電玩角色JINX，因與自己性格相近，喜愛破壞但忠於本能。<br />\n<br />\n香港大學現代語言及文化學院王向華副教授，研究日本流行文化多年，對於雪月這樣的cosplayer有如此看法：「對她而言，真實的她就在角色中，我較強調以他們的目光看世界，而非我們的目光，然後覺得他們很離譜。」雪月因身形而被圍攻沒有資格cosplay，王教授則勉勵她道：「主流社會正正定義了怎樣是吸引的女人、性感的女人，而權力便隱藏於定義中。但每個年代的定義很任意、飄忽，所以你只要不信奉這一套，知道這是偏見就可以。」"},{"pid":"ccf3e1e337cf4a374e6c637283a61c000951b662","tid":1076971,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20160119/large/18grennew2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160119%2Flarge%2F18grennew2.jpg&h=e9ed94f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現時雪月一個月「私影」兩次，相比初時一星期五天的高峰期，現在少得多。"},{"pid":"8c5b96b65e7d9e5c6907a775626514c7ed74cf63","tid":1076971,"uid":219216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"私影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbf7080c4babdea5f557269f9cba47cc30ab9a6","tid":1076971,"uid":32439,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPiZfWP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPiZfWP.gif&h=5a29fabd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80a9794d0c6f0624d0ecd1584ef144128cad76fa","tid":1076971,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"講到尾咪又係唔肯減<br />\n<br />\n點解你咁撚肥<br />\n因為食野亂咁黎～"},{"pid":"b24880c54b3ae484137747077c220310177ac0c5","tid":1076971,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:06:48.000Z","msg":"佢cos 微辣嗰個雲吞咪得"},{"pid":"da30d0d5a46b6fc1dda0883b9b3fc0b0714d1e1f","tid":1076971,"uid":29080,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rc-evo.com/xbbs/data/attachment/forum/day_100218/1002181616b0e312c0e29a4ddf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frc-evo.com%2Fxbbs%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2Fday_100218%2F1002181616b0e312c0e29a4ddf.jpg&h=4cdf32f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b68f3b478cfbabeb643bc1897aa0bc2e1a79ab5","tid":1076971,"uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da30d0d5a46b6fc1dda0883b9b3fc0b0714d1e1f","tid":1076971,"uid":29080,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rc-evo.com/xbbs/data/attachment/forum/day_100218/1002181616b0e312c0e29a4ddf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frc-evo.com%2Fxbbs%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2Fday_100218%2F1002181616b0e312c0e29a4ddf.jpg&h=4cdf32f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"原來真係cos緊呢部機<br />\n仲以為係啲咩XP娘添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"